{"type": "article", "id": 17322, "title": "带有溜边的鼠标垫", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-10T06:20:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702101211W9ERXNmuSTYIaviV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国洛杉矶的工作室 This Is Ground 发现人们移动鼠标时，手腕常常在桌子边缘，并不舒服。于是设计了这个带有溜边的鼠标垫，桌面上是长方形的垫子，带有一个长 12 英寸的刻度标记，下面连接了一条边，挂在桌子的侧面以帮助固定，以减少手腕在边缘的摩擦，是非常贴心的细节设计。售价 100 美元，<a href=\"http://thisisground.com/products/mouse-pad-pro?mc_cid=b1de8bf525&amp;mc_eid=13e5a129c9&amp;variant=8042849413\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144427QUkatX5NxRJmvnO8.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144428X4MFhoYeDtPUT95G.jpg\" width=\"1012\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699605\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144428L7BGcZy42Q50I1nO.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}